Class DataSelectReader

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    edu.sc.seis.seisFile.MSeedQueryReader

    public class DataSelectReader
extends edu.sc.seis.seisFile.StringMSeedQueryReader
    The data select reader reads data from the web services. This class a based on the edu.sc.seis.seisFile.dataSelectWS.DataSelectReader class with minor changes for Swarm.
    Author:
    Kevin Frechette (ISTI)
